commentTextItems.html: launches into the shot, hits over mid on, Walsh comes running in, picks up the catch there

commentPostTextItems.html: West Indies have won, by 70 runs
We thought we bowled well... it is just the batting this is not the best pitch in the world, but you can't complain the big match is on Tuesday....
Brian Lara, to pick up the winners cheque
The total that we scored was defendable
Dillon bowled pretty well and also batted well to give us extra runs in the end
Man of the match, adjudicator Clyde Walcott goes to... Sherwin Campbell for his batting
That is it folks, good bye

commentTextItems.html: outside the off, edged to thrid man boundary!
flighted, beats him, off the pads to short third man
